src:
Vídeo mostra alguns dos momentos do ‘Ilhatrónica’, no Mercado dos Lavradores
Bispo do Funchal recordou importância do baptismo para uma vida e morte em Cristo
02 Nov 2019, 02:49 by Sandra S. Gonçalves






O Mercado dos Lavradores recebeu ontem a 4.ª edição do ‘Ilhatrónica’, um evento integrado no roteiro de espectáculos musicais ‘NOS Apresenta’, que trouxe à Madeira os DJ’s Vibe e Moullinex.
text:
Video shows some of the moments of ‘Ilhatrónica’, at the Farmers Market
Bishop of Funchal recalled importance of baptism for a life and death in Christ
02 Nov 2019, 02:49 by Sandra S. Gonçalves






The Farmers Market received yesterday the 4th edition of ‘Ilhatrónica’, an event included in the script of musical shows ‘NOS Presa’, which brought to DJs Vibe and Moullinex to Madeira.
